official_title: A resolution authorizing the printing of additional copies of the Senate hearings on the nomination of Gerald R. Ford to be Vice President.

summary.text: Provides that there be printed for the use of the Committee on Rules and Administration additional copies of its hearings on the nomination of Gerald R. Ford to be Vice President of the United States in such quantity as shall not exceed the statutory $1,200 limitation.

titles.title: A resolution authorizing the printing of additional copies of the Senate hearings on the nomination of Gerald R. Ford to be Vice President.
